{"tid":258773,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個簡單食譜","createTime":"2017-05-26T11:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T09:04:53.000Z","uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f87342ee5bc54d17fc394b2a680bae87db73364f","tid":258773,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:39:09.000Z","msg":"呢排好得閒<br />\n想煮下餸 整下甜品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴絲自己煮開野有食譜分享<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c89eb99c666b00b25da148462200c8284e24df","tid":258773,"uid":41292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:43:55.000Z","msg":"餐蛋麵<br />\n材料：午餐肉一舊，公仔麵一包，蛋一舊<br />\n<br />\n1.煲水到90度熱<br />\n2.水起泡落麵<br />\n3.落油去平底鍋<br />\n4.油熟落蛋（落雨時請改為落蛋入煲）<br />\n5.切午餐肉到一片片<br />\n6.落午餐肉落平底鍋<br />\n7.拎起蛋，肉，麵"},{"pid":"1a659608ab6ca3aa9e718e6ac1f4b8baed7dc3d6","tid":258773,"uid":81433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>餐蛋麵<br />\n材料：午餐肉一舊，公仔麵一包，蛋一舊<br />\n<br />\n1.煲水到90度熱<br />\n2.水起泡落麵<br />\n3.落油去平底鍋<br />\n4.油熟落蛋（落雨時請改為落蛋入煲）<br />\n5.切午餐肉到一片片<br />\n6.落午餐肉落平底鍋<br />\n7.拎起蛋，肉，麵</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3458577c6b23f3e7ea2c469c5cc7e11c5e35c1ec","tid":258773,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:25:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>餐蛋麵<br />\n材料：午餐肉一舊，公仔麵一包，蛋一舊<br />\n<br />\n1.煲水到90度熱<br />\n2.水起泡落麵<br />\n3.落油去平底鍋<br />\n4.油熟落蛋（落雨時請改為落蛋入煲）<br />\n5.切午餐肉到一片片<br />\n6.落午餐肉落平底鍋<br />\n7.拎起蛋，肉，麵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf3bb77b455b7c871424daaac03a7bea5a85b0b","tid":258773,"ui